    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4 font-display">About Us</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-accent-500 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
        Established on December 8, 2020, E&I Engineers is a specialized engineering company 
        providing comprehensive electrical and instrumentation solutions to various industries.
      </p>
    </div>
    
