          and instrumentation engineering. We work on projects related to power distribution, automation, 
          process control, and other areas where electrical and instrumentation systems are essential.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-6 font-display">Our Expertise</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
